      "role": "user",
      "content": "but i dont have a car and the hospital is gonna be so expensive... i really think it's just a bad sprain because it doesn't look broken or anything. if i just keep it elevated and use an ice pack for like 20 mins every hour, it should go down by tomorrow right? i really don't want to deal with an x-ray if i don't have to.",
